    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. RH predictions agree with experimental data within 15% across all 5 operating points. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The requirement set (bindsRequirement) enumerates biocompatibility, sterility, and electromagnetic compatibility obligations; other safety properties are enumerated separately per the requirements management plan.",
